Calculator CodeAlpha Project.
This is a simple yet functional Calculator built using HTML, CSS and JavaScript. It provides a clean and user-friendly interface for performing basic arithmetic operations such as addition, subtraction,
multiplication, and division.

Features:
  ->Intuitive and responsive design.
  ->Supports basic arithmetic operations(addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division)
  ->Real-time display of input and results.
  ->Clear button to reset calculations.
  ->Interactive button effects for better user experience.

This project was developed as part of the CodeAlpha Internship Program to enhance front-end development skills and improve UI/UX design.

  
